---
title: Thai Spiced Pork Noodles with scallion and bell peppers
description: The pork mince in this recipe is seasoned with a beautiful blend of Thai-inspired spices. You might pick out hints of lemongrass, galangal powder and kafir lime leaves as you tuck into this tasty noodle dish.
